description:
Versatile pants for everyday winter adventures or hiking through the snow. The tough fabric and DWR (durable water repellent) finish sheds light rain and snowfall.Water-resistant soft shell fabric is made of a durable blend of nylon and polyester with a hint of spandex for range of movement.Soft brushed lining is bonded to the exterior fabric.Fixed waistband with belt loops and hidden adjustable waistband for a perfect fit.Zippered fly with a snap closure.2 front slash pockets and 1 thigh pocket with hook-and-loop closure to hold small essentials.Articulated knees and gusseted crotch for easy movement.

